start.label: not all it's cracked up to be

examples.en: She exceeded our expectations.

The company has expectations of making a profit next year.

He had surpassed all our expectations.
She pitched her expectations too high.
His performance exceeded our expectations.
The price quotes exceeded our expectations.
Gina has succeeded beyond our expectations.
He had been amused so long with vain expectations.
His performance did not live up to our expectations.
This study concerns couples' expectations of marriage.
